# share/cowrie sample guide
#
# This directory can host Cowrie shared data files (custom artifacts,
# optional text resources, and reusable fake content files).
#
# Example files you can add here:
# - distro-release.txt (fake OS release metadata)
# - package-list.txt  (fake installed package inventory)
# - legal-banner.txt  (fake warning/legal text)
#
# Example package-list.txt snippet:
#   openssh-server 1:8.2p1-4ubuntu0.10
#   python3 3.8.10-0ubuntu1~20.04
#   nginx 1.18.0-0ubuntu1.6
#
# Keep values internally consistent across honeyfs and txtcmds outputs.
